<node id="&quot;ACETYLCHOLINE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Acetylcholine is a specific excitatory neurotransmitter that is blocked by philanthotoxins, preventing the transmission of signals in nerve cells."</data>
