<node id="&quot;MEDICARE ADVANTAGE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Medicare Advantage is a type of United States health insurance program within Medicare that provides managed health care plans."&lt;SEP&gt;"Medicare Advantage is a type of health insurance program within Medicare, offering managed care plans to beneficiaries as an alternative to Original Medicare Parts A and B."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-3131beff8473ac110bb6fe240fe57dbf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e33a24d622f5803fe7958f7fed2670a3</data>
