<node id="&quot;CIGNA&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"CIGNA is a Managed Care entity involved in Case Management and Utilization Review decisions."&lt;SEP&gt;"CIGNA is a Managed Care entity mentioned in the Aetna Health Inc. v. Davila case, subject to the legal duty of care according to the THCLA."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-3131beff8473ac110bb6fe240fe57dbf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9da95c787d3fcf42b176c577484a8ab</data>
