<node id="&quot;SUPREME COURT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The Supreme Court granted the federal government the 'Interstate Commerce' power, which was used to enact ERISA."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Supreme Court ruled in the Aetna Health Inc. v. Davila case, limiting the scope of the THCLA and its enforcement in certain circumstances."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-3131beff8473ac110bb6fe240fe57dbf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9da95c787d3fcf42b176c577484a8ab</data>
