  <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Schistocerca nitens can be found in Texas."&lt;SEP&gt;"Texas is a state in the United States, containing Irving, the headquarters of Flowserve Corporation."&lt;SEP&gt;"Texas is a state where the grasshopper is native."&lt;SEP&gt;"Texas is the state where the Texas Healthcare Liability Act (THCLA) was enacted and where the Aetna Health Inc. v. Davila case took place."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-929f86da74ae1e3ce3a1356565985752&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c787f4ff2d5af14f3559361b72b3f39f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3131beff8473ac110bb6fe240fe57dbf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d6b44c59c6f7913c12a139520a184d15</data>
