  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The Texas Healthcare Liability Act (THCLA) imposed a legal duty of care on Case Management and Utilization Review decisions by Managed Care entities according to the laws of Texas."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-3131beff8473ac110bb6fe240fe57dbf</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CASE MANAGEMENT AND UTILIZATION REVIEW&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Case Management and Utilization Review are processes involving decisions by Managed Care entities such as CIGNA and Aetna, subject to legal duties of care according to state laws."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-e9da95c787d3fcf42b176c577484a8ab</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 21}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 108}]</data>
</node>
