  <data key="d1">"Italians of Ethiopia are emigrants and colonists from Italy who moved to live in Ethiopia and their descendants."&lt;SEP&gt;"Italians of Ethiopia refers to emigrants and colonists from Italy who moved to live in Ethiopia starting from the 19th century, along with their descendants. They played a significant role in the exchange of ideas, farming techniques, education, and technology with Ethiopians."</data>
